title: ETNIES PRESENTS THE FRONT GIRLS AT HEVY 2011: EPISODE 1
description: Hevy 2011 kicked off with a big bang and the Friday ended with a banging party at the etnies and Front stage. With the crowd just waking up after a hard night on the festival, etnies present Hevy 2011 episode one. In this episode one, the amazing front girls talk to "Lower than Atlantis" and we see the crowd having a great time at the first day of the festival.
